ustom fields values not applied if there is space after dot.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed: Proposal editor not applying some html styles becuase of XSS filter.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed: Menu builder not opening fontawesome icon selector dropdown.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed: New recurring invoice or copy invoice auto marked to cancel overdue reminders.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed: Select custom field when its checked disable customer to edit not applied.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed: Invoice dashboard stats percent including Cancelled invoices too.<\/li>\n<li>UI Improvements.<\/li>\n<li>Minor bugs fixed.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Please refer to this blog post for additional\u00a0info about the changes. Changes made in the main Perfex CRM theme. Added Dropbox file choser for Tasks, Invoices, Estimates, Proposals, Leads, Customer attachments, Contracts Added ability to select\/deselect all project expenses while invoicing project. Added option to update all staff permissions that using specific role when updating [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[23],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-763","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-changelog"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/763","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=763"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/763\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.